title: Dihun janai dibosa
lyrics:
Dihun janai dibosa
Jwngni mwnse jarimin
Be jarimin dihun jandwng
Subungkhou fwjakhangnw -2
(A)
Jwng sibigwn khouse janan
“Kristoni gaham batra-2”
Jwng rwjabgwn Kristni methai
“Subungkhou fwjakhangnw-2” -2
(B)
Khonsaibwdwng be dibosa
“Buhumni subung fwrkhou-2”
Somai hwdwng be dibosa
“Geremsa khwmsali khou-2”
